Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:36.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:47.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:55.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:03:01.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:08.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:12.43,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:22.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:29.51,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:36.26,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:47.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:55.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:36.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在傷害別人之前　不必強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:47.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說著她低下頭　在黑夜裡哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:55.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷黏合在一起　渾身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:03:01.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停　卻沒有傘來遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:08.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:12.43,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰鬥才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:22.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的彼岸所見到的　是五彩光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:29.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那時蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:36.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　雖說不能像鳥兒一樣自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:47.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害別人之後的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:55.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地閉上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:07.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#20  亞琉·利塔娜\N{\fs22\fsp28}　{\fsp1}A New Return{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀的位置？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為改革者的你都不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我知道在哪裡  你們又打算把吠陀怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀本來就是為給我們使用而製造的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼告訴我  你們準備用吠陀來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞設立這個計劃的真正目的又是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了即將到來的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將到來的對話？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是人類的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也不見得是萬能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是也被我們抓住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是故意的話…又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 菲露特…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利塔娜小姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉她怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打傷了拉塞  把米蕾娜當作人質…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利塔娜小姐說自己是改革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉她？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.36,0:01:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有個什麼閃失的話  人質的性命就不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同型號的我和亞琉的思想能相互交流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉  接下來按照預定計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內系統被…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利…利塔娜小姐  還是停下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話  大家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想從這裡過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼知道這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為只有你們能用腦量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內系統被病毒感染了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成兩路去找米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐回艦橋去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死  亞琉在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲小姐來了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把你給忘了  C level的腦量子波使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未完成的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切的元兇就是你們  上校的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清榮先生  斯托拉托斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  亞琉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想丟下我離開嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起走嗎？  能看到世界的改革哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Right  這事算我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還另外贈送Cherudim一台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來受你關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用真打吧？ 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人質被奪回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成女性的樣子就這麼感情用事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉要用小型艇脫離嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這系統怎麼這樣？ 太隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三艙門自動打開  後部艙門也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Cherudim和OO去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉口跟李本茲說去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩  抱歉得以奪回O-Raiser為優先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了TRANS-AM了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備讓這部機體受損嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有優秀的戰術預報員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Raiser  對接模式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統被OO強行介入…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟洛克恩說的一樣  你們離萬能還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  O-Raiser就放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  還是想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留點紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Raiser的輸出功率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要向我開槍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來  亞琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉·利塔娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍啊…瞄準開槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了什麼在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼…加入卡塔隆  加入Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:09:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒出息的男人  萊爾·迪蘭地！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的覺悟就是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾·迪蘭地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的愛你  萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你身體不適  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是用新藥比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馬克  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你抑制肆虐的體內細胞異常的藥物是為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你向我請求的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現沒有紛爭的統一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了向Gundam報你雙親的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你很期待哦  這部Regnant也是特意為你帶來的
